ruby-cairo
------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for the cairo graphics engine.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  libcairo2-1.6.4-1
  ruby-1.8.7_p22-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-20080523-2
  cygport-0.3.13-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.23a-2

Canonical website:
  http://cairographics.org/

Canonical download:
  http://cairographics.org/releases/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ruby-cairo-1.6.3-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ruby-cairo-1.6.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.6.3-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.6.3-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

