Port Notes:

----- version 1.6.3-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 1.6.1-1 -----
Version bump for cairo-1.6.

----- version 1.4.1-1 -----
Version bump for cairo-1.4.  Included rdoc.

----- version 1.2.0-1 -----
Version bump.  Changed package name from rcairo for consistency with 
the ruby-gnome2 packages.

----- version 1.0.0-2 -----
Include link library in binary package for ruby-gnome2 cairo support.

----- version 1.0.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


